reviews.title: EXCELLENT APPS
reviews.comment: Clear illustration and easy to understand instruction.  Excellent apps. Thank you.
reviews.author: Wen Lk

reviews.title: Excellent!
reviews.comment: This is the best resource for Tsubo points I\'ve found in apps market! Thorough, efficient, and easy to use. Thank you Devs!!!(licensed massage therapist)
reviews.author: Jennifer Oliver

reviews.title: Very handy!!
reviews.comment: Nice app, glad it\'s in English too. Most effective,  I can really feel the difference!
reviews.author: Ahnya del Rosario

reviews.title: detailed
reviews.comment: but pointless, because nobody has time and patience to look stuff up off long lists
reviews.author: lalo lalouve

reviews.title: GREAT in two LANGUAGES
reviews.comment: Version 2.5 update made me very happy.  Now I can choose languages, English (\350\213\261\350\252\236) or Japanese (\346\227\245\346\234\254\350\252\236). Thank you very much for your quick response and  update.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Very handy and to the point
reviews.comment: The positions are explained very well.. Also, their benefits.. Please add some more categories
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great idea
reviews.comment: but Introduction and search functions are too big on my phone-it is difficult to view the symptoms and tsubopoints! Also, would appreciate more conditions being available. Thank you.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Would like an english version or option
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Not a study app
reviews.comment: Boy does this app suck. Too much repetition in the points suggested for different symptoms. I guess if you just want to know which points to palpate for a few basic things, it\'s not bad. After all it its free. ATTN STUDENTS OF ACUPUNCTURE, this is not a study app.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Pleasantly surprised
reviews.comment: A really useful easy to apply app. Only problem is that the text is VERY faint so I struggle to read.  Can you fix this?
reviews.author: AnSapphire Gael
